trans-unit.source: Exposes a data item in an <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items*> collection to [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Expõe um item de dados num <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items*>coleção para [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items*>

trans-unit.source: Data items that are not also <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> types do not have children; however, they can have a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> tree and a corresponding [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] tree.
trans-unit.target: Itens de dados que não são também <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>tipos não tem elementos subordinados; no entanto, pode ter um <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>árvore e um correspondente [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] árvore.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement>

trans-unit.source: For example, a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBox> can have a collection of strings that contain data items.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, um <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBox>pode ter um conjunto de cadeias que contêm itens de dados.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBox>

trans-unit.source: When those items are processed by an <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> for visualization, a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> tree is created for them.
trans-unit.target: Quando os itens são processados por um <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>para visualização, um <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>árvore é criada para os mesmos.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>

trans-unit.source: This tree can have a corresponding [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] tree.
trans-unit.target: Esta árvore pode ter um correspondente [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] árvore.

trans-unit.source: After the tree is created, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] merges the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> tree into a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] tree.
trans-unit.target: Após a criação de árvore, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] une o <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>árvore para um [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] árvore.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement>

trans-unit.source: ItemAutomationPeer works with its <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> counterpart, if it exists, to obtain more information about the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> tree.
trans-unit.target: ItemAutomationPeer funciona com o respetivo <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>homólogo, se existir, para obter mais informações sobre o <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>árvore.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement>

trans-unit.source: Only visible data items, or more precisely, the corresponding <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> trees, have this dualism.
trans-unit.target: Apenas os itens de dados visível ou mais precisamente, correspondente <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>árvores, ter esta dualism.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement>

trans-unit.source: Non-visible data items, which have no corresponding <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> trees, have only one ItemAutomationPeer.
trans-unit.target: Itens de dados não visível, que têm não correspondentes <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>árvores, ter apenas um ItemAutomationPeer.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement>
